column1: #Text=UEFA Euro 2016 , day 13 : Iceland-Austria , Hungary-Poland , Italy-Republic of Ireland and Sweden-Belgium
#Text=The headline mistakenly reads Poland where it should read Portugal , which is correctly reflected by the article itself .
#Text=On Wednesday in UEFA Euro 2016 , Iceland defeated Austria 2 – 1 , Hungary drew against Portugal 3 – 3 , Italy lost 0 – 1 to Republic of Ireland and Belgium defeated Sweden 1 – 0 .
#Text=Hungary , Italy , Republic of Ireland , Belgium , Portugal and Iceland qualified for the Last 16 knockout phase .
#Text=File photo of Cristiano Ronaldo , who scored a brace against Hungary as the match ended in a goalless draw .
#Text=Jón Daði Böðvarsson scored an early goal putting Iceland in front .
#Text=Even this match seemed likely to end in 1 – 1 after Alessandro Schöpf scored an equaliser in the 60th minute , but Arnór Ingvi Traustason scored the late match-winning goal for Iceland .
#Text=Iceland qualified for Last 16 knockout phase , while Austria was eliminated winning only one point in a goalless draw against Portugal .
#Text=Hungary were 1 – 0 up in the 19th minute as Zoltán Gera found the net .
#Text=Balázs Dzsudzsák put The Hungarians in front , scoring the second goal in the 47th minute .
#Text=In the 50th minute , Portuguese captain Cristiano Ronaldo scored and , in doing so , became the first player to score in four different Euro tournaments .
#Text=Five minutes later , Dzsudzsák scored the third goal for Hungary .
#Text=In the 62nd minute , Ronaldo scored for Portugal and the match ended in a 3 – 3 draw , making it the highest scoring match in this tournament till now .
#Text=Portugal 's all three matches ended in a draw in the group stage .
#Text=Both Hungary and Portugal have qualified for the Last 16 knockout phase .
#Text=Italy had qualified for the Last 16 knockout phase winning the previous match against Sweden .
#Text=But Robbie Brady scored a late goal which helped Republic of Ireland qualify for the knockout phase as well .
#Text=In the 84th minute , Radja Nainggolan scored the only goal of the match for the Belgians .
#Text=While Belgium qualified for the knockout phase , Sweden has been eliminated , and with that loss , Swedish captain Zlatan Ibrahimović failed to score in the fourth Euro tournament .
#Text=He had announced that he would quit his international duty after Sweden finished this tournament .
#Text=Italy v Republic of Ireland 21:00 June 22 , 2016 ( UTC+2 )
#Text=Salvatore Sirigu 39 ' Andrea Barzagli 78 ' Simone Zaza 87 ' Lorenzo Insigne 90+1 ' 0 – 0 ( HT )
